Package: PfRecur
Title: Probabilistic classification of Plasmodium falciparum recurrences
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Somya", "Mehra", email="somya@tropmedres.ac", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Aimee", "Taylor", role = c("cph")),
    person("Mallika", "Imwong", role = c("cph")),
    person("Nicholas", "White", role = c("cph")),
    person("James", "Watson", role = c("cph")))
Description: Computes the (analytical) posterior distribution of the number of 
  recrudescent vs newly-inoculated clones within a recurrent isolate, based
  on bulk genotypic data, under a Bayesian framework.
